    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a museum-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in iconic Laguna Seca Blue. This specimen features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333hp through six individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS variable valve timing. The powertrain is mated to a crisp Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M Variable Differential Lock. Mechanically flawless, the chassis has undergone proactive subframe reinforcement and a rod bearing service to ensure long-term structural integrity. The suspension retains its factory-spec damping with zero bushing deflection. This is a collector-grade example with original paint depth and a pristine interior, offering a visceral, high-RPM driving experience rarely found in such preserved condition.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
